<section id='build-tools'>
  <title>Build Tools</title>

  <para>
    This section provides a short list of some of the important
    &lsb;-related tools, along with references to other parts of this
    document where they are discussed in greater detail.
  </para>
  <variablelist>
    <varlistentry>
      <term>lsbcc</term>
      <listitem>
        <para>Not yet provided by the &lsb; organization.  See <quote><link linkend="sec-wrapper" endterm="sec-wrapper.title"/></quote>
        </para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>

    <varlistentry>
      <term>rpmbuild</term>
      <listitem>
        <para>Part of the &rpm; package maintained by the
          &lsb; organization. Used to create &rpm; packages. See
          <quote><link linkend="sec-packaging-tool"
          endterm="sec-packaging-tool.title"/></quote></para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>

    <varlistentry>
      <term>chroot build environment</term>
      <listitem>
        <para>Provided by the &lsbdev; package. See <quote><link
              linkend="sec-chroot" endterm="sec-chroot.title"/></quote></para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
  </variablelist>

</section>

